Description: Provides tools for evaluating and ranking missing data imputation methods using proper scoring rules. Implements the energy-I-Score from Näf et al. (2025) <arXiv:2507.11297> and DR-I-Score introduced in Näf et al. (2022) <arXiv:2106.03742>. Supports deterministic, stochastic and multiple imputation methods for numerical and mixed datasets.
